# FashionStore
Fashion Store is a responsive, single-page e-commerce website built using HTML and CSS. It is designed to showcase various fashion options in a user-friendly and visually appealing layout. The project simulates a modern fashion brand's landing page and demonstrates front-end development skills through clean structure and styling.
👗 Fashion Store – E-Commerce Landing Page
A stylish and responsive one-page e-commerce website built with HTML and CSS. This project simulates the homepage of a fictional online clothing store called Fashion Store, designed to showcase fashion options, highlight upcoming sales, and promote user engagement with a clean and appealing interface.

