📝 Overview
Fashion Store is a front-end web project focused on UI/UX design using basic web technologies. The goal was to create a responsive landing page that represents an online fashion store. It includes:

A navbar for navigation

Fashion item listings

A shopping-time promotional banner

Upcoming sales in tabular format

A benefits list to attract users

A clean footer

This project is ideal for beginners looking to improve their HTML and CSS skills.

✅ Features
Responsive navigation bar

Grid-based fashion cards

Call-to-action shopping banner

HTML table for upcoming sales

Highlighted benefits list

Mobile-friendly and easy-to-navigate layout

Footer with copyright

🧰 Tech Stack
HTML5 – Markup structure

CSS3 – Styling and layout

(No frameworks or JavaScript used – pure HTML/CSS project)

